name: Callbox Australia
overview:
B2B Lead generation and appointment setting company that specializes in generating targeted and qualified business sales leads through telemarketing in Australia.

“Callbox is a full service sales and marketing solutions provider specialising in contact center services to generate business leads for companies looking to enhance their market reach and productivity. Based in New South Wales, Australia, we generate leads and set appointments for local sales organisations in Sydney, Melbourne, Brisbane, Perth, and other major commercial centres throughout the country.

Established in 2006, Callbox provides lead generation and appointment setting services to companies operating in business-to-business marketplaces. Our extensive cross-industry experience enables us to work flexibly, and adapt to varying business priorities and market demands. We combine industry expertise and talent to produce highly-qualified business leads even in extremely saturated and competitive Australian markets.

As a world-class full service call centre agency, Callbox is the biggest provider of contact centre services in Australia and throughout the Asia Pacific Region. We handle specific telemarketing functions (e.g. cold calling, event marketing, or following up on a mailshot), or assist in the entire sales process – from making cold calls to setting appointments and closing sales in behalf of our clients. Either way, our clients can rest assured that they are employing motivated and experienced professionals whose reputation rely on delivering results.”
